reviewText: What's not to love about this?!!
Can't get enough of this DVD. I've watched it every night for nearly a month. So entertaining and so much talent. I really wish it was an album! I am in Love!

Very good concert. Good video, good Audio. You can see a few songs from this concert on Youtube, but seeing the whole integral concert is something else. Shipped from the UK.. Had expected it to be in PAL(which we can play), but turned out it was NTSC. Even better. Great service, fast shipping. Very happy..
Fantastic concert video. Gary Barlow is a rare and very talented musical artist. He is a pleasure to watch and its a feel good kind of night when ever I watch it!
As always, Gary delivers a great concert. I enjoyed the oldies mixed with his new stuff. Well done!

This is a must see DVD great quality picture and a lovely concert. and lovely to see kids there and beautiful songs even Sing the song he co-wrote for the Queen Jubilee concert and it was nice to see the local high school choir singing that song. Brilliant.
Great concert with Gary at the top of his game.
Got my stuff very fast. Great conditions on both items. Couldn't be happier all around. Awesome dvd and cd.
